        "created_at": "2018-09-21T08:26:32.006Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Are there any plans to support building static library for foundationdb (like libfdb_c.a)?</p>\n<p>using dynamic library can be very problematic when using a container environment because binaries (eg. written in go) cannot be statically linked.</p>",
